text: Zach Sproule (born 12 May 1998) is an Australian rules footballer who plays for the Greater Western Sydney in the Australian Football League (AFL). He joined the club as a Category B rookie selections coming from the Giant's Academy. He made his senior debut against Western Bulldogs in round 22 of the 2019 season. ==References== ==External links== * * * Category:Greater Western Sydney Giants players Category:Australian rules footballers from New South Wales Category:Murray Bushrangers players Category:1998 births Category:Living people
